Cactus Code Thorn EOS_Polytrope
Authors    : Ian Hawke
CVS info   : $Header$
--------------------------------------------------------------------------

Purpose of the thorn:

This is a "faked" polytropic equation of state. It is designed to work through the CactusEOS interface. The EoS reads

Pressure = eos_k * rho ** (eos_gamma)

The specific internal energy is given by the assumption of a perfect fluid.